Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:56.78,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:171615,176787}If we lose today's battle, our enemies\Nwill head straight for Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.41,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:176787,180415}Today's battle is not only\Nabout the fate of France,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:06.42,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:180415,186421}it is a battle that will determine\Nthe fate of Emperor Napoleon III.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.75,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:186630,188757}I expect all of you\Nto take this with the upmost severity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.05,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:189675,191051}I am counting on you,\Ngentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.42,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:191343,192427}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.22,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:200477,202229}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.18,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:202229,204189}Be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.27,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:204189,206275}What are our chances of win?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:29.27,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:206275,209278}I don't know. But what I know\Nis that losing is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.99,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:210696,213991}Back in Paris, I have\Nmy parents and two sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:37.61,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:213991,217619}I cannot put my family at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.53,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:255449,257534}Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.45,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:257534,259453}Settle down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.53,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:260412,261538}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.75,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:263290,266752}You don't have\Nto worry about Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.96,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:266752,269963}She's already getting\Ndressed for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.09,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:270547,274092}Even she will not remain\Na tomboy forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.26,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:278430,281266}Ms. Jeanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.10,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:281975,283101}Ms. Jeanne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.81,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:283101,284811}Did you find Ms. Isabelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.85,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:284811,287856}Yes, she's playing\Nat the fountain in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.94,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:288440,290943}She doesn't think of us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.98,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:290943,293987}Make her stop whatever she's doing,\Nand let's prepare her for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.65,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:294363,295656}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:02.74,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:298575,302746}Today she is supposed to make her social\Ndebut. What a troublesome little lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.71,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:307584,309711}I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.29,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:309711,312297}This thing is way too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.71,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:312297,315717}Ms. Isabelle has become\Nvery beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.80,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:315717,317803}Take a look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.34,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:317803,320347}You're no longer that\Nmischievous little tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:37.53,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:335070,337531}This is… me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.32,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:337531,340325}That's right.\NYou're an elegant lady now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.74,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:341660,344746}{\i1}An elegant… lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.59,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:358260,359594}{\i1}An elegant lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:18.44,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:373525,378447}Tell me, Jeanne, who is the\Nfairer maiden, me, or my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.28,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:378905,381283}Compared to Ms. Geneviève?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.86,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:381867,383869}Oh, that look says it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.53,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:383869,385537}Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:28.04,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:385537,388040}My sister is in another\Nleague, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.66,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:388040,389666}What ever was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.16,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:390083,392169}No, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.04,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:392169,395047}Ms. Geneviève has her elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.92,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:395047,397924}However, you, Ms. Isabelle\Nhave your young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.55,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:397924,399551}It's a good weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.21,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:400010,401219}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.43,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:401219,403430}I could get used to such flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.39,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:404973,407392}It's not flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.64,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:407392,408643}Right, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.18,Default,Maid,0,0,0,,{TIME:408643,410187}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.81,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:410604,412814}All right, let me\Nshow myself to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.61,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:415025,416610}I wonder what she'll say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.20,Default,Jeanne,0,0,0,,{TIME:419863,423200}Oh, dear. She's still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.84,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:441760,443845}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.76,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:444596,446765}Sister, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.93,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:447265,448934}Oh? Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.14,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:452104,454147}Look what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.27,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:454147,455273}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:38.44,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:455273,458443}When you wear a dress for a party, you need\Nto make more careful movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.99,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:460362,464991}Here I was, finally trying\Nto show you something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.20,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:464991,466201}I'm such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.78,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:466201,467786}That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.03,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:467786,470038}Isabelle, you're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.87,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:470497,472874}Do you really think so?\NThank you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:56.46,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:472874,476461}By the way, Maestro, are you going\Nto the ball with us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.92,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:476670,479923}Yes, I will play\Nthe piano this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.30,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:480048,482300}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:09.97,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:482801,489975}Isabelle, why don't you show your\Nwonderful dress to Mother and Father now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.43,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:489975,493437}I need to continue\Nwith my piano lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:22.82,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:497607,502821}Mother and Father have been eagerly\Nwaiting for you all this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.32,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:503655,505323}You're right.\NI'm sorry I disturbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:28.99,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:507951,508994}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.20,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:508994,512205}Oops, that won't do.\NI'm a proper lady now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.04,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:514624,516042}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.50,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:520172,523508}That brings memories.\NShe makes me remember my own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.38,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:524384,526386}The day I made my social debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.01,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:527012,529014}Social debuts and balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.85,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:529014,532851}France is now\Nin the middle of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.85,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:532851,535854}I don't understand\Nwhat the rich are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.52,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:539149,540525}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.27,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:540775,543278}But, Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.40,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:543278,546406}The feeling of love\Nremains constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.03,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:547532,550035}Let's not go in\Nthat direction, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.53,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:551036,554539}I'm nothing but\Na poor piano teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.33,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:554539,556333}The worlds we live in\Nare too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.04,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:556541,558043}Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.17,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:558043,561171}Besides, you have\Nan ideal fiancé, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.04,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:561171,564049}That was my Father's decision.\NYou are the one I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.21,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:564049,565217}Geneviève!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.46,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:565717,567469}Some mountains\Ncannot be climbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.38,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:567469,568386}I will not accept that.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:23.60,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:623608,623608}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:639374,640834}{\i1}A social debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.46,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:640834,643461}{\i1}She was about to meet\Nthe high society for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:49.13,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:643461,649134}{\i1}Isabelle couldn't suppress her heart beat,\Nfull of expectations and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.80,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:652971,654806}We will be there any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.89,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:655724,657892}There is no need\Nto feel stiff, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.33,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:678705,680332}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.59,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:685337,688590}This evening is your first step\Ninto high society, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.59,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:688590,690592}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.43,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:698975,701436}Mother, I'm anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.56,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:704064,706566}My dear Isabelle.\NI was just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.81,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:706566,708818}Where has your\Nusual bravery gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.94,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:709694,710945}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.53,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:711363,713531}Please take my hand,\NMs. Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:55.36,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:713740,715367}Thank you, Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.74,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:716284,717744}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.24,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:720163,722248}{\i1}Ms. Geneviève…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.67,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:728713,730674}{\i1}Ms. Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:28.35,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:744604,748358}Léon and Marie Rostain\Nwith their daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.75,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:769671,771756}This is the high society…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.55,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:771756,774551}{\i1}This is the high society, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.59,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:775427,778596}{\i1}From the moment of her\Ndebut in the high society,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.93,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:778596,781933}{\i1}Isabelle's beauty\Ncaptured people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.22,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:783685,785228}You're so beautiful, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.56,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:786312,787564}Mr. Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.94,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:788189,789941}You have grown into a fine lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.82,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:792569,795822}Tell me, Isabelle,\Nwould you say yes to a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.32,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:795822,799325}Or am I not worthy,\Nas your sister's fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.28,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:799617,802287}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.78,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:802287,803788}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.08,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:803788,805081}You can dance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.96,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:808251,809961}Here, Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.83,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:811463,812839}Oh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.09,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:816551,818094}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:01.40,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:838239,841409}{\i1}That dance was\Nlike a dream for Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:11.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:842368,851085}{\i1}Isabelle was strangely attracted\Nto her sister Geneviève's fiancé, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.30,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:860553,862305}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.89,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:862305,863890}May I have a dance now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.22,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:865642,867227}You will be drafted soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.18,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:867644,870188}I shall go back to my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.73,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:870188,871731}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.90,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:876528,877904}Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.74,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:879197,882742}Isabelle, what's wrong?\NDid you forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.87,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:883034,885870}You bullied me all the time\Nwhen we were kids, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.62,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:885870,888623}We lived next to each other\Nin Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.54,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:889123,890542}Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.21,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:890542,892210}It's you, Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.96,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:896297,897966}{\i1}This is dangerous!\NI'm going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.51,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:900176,902512}{\i1}Wait for me! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.47,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:909561,911479}{\i1}What a big catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.27,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:913273,915275}{\i1}It's so tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.06,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:915567,917068}{\i1}Jean, I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.23,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:917068,918236}{\i1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.07,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:918236,919070}{\i1}Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.61,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:920613,921614}{\i1}Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.45,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:924409,926452}{\i1}You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:30.79,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:927078,930790}{\i1}Hey, Isabelle, will you be\Nmy bride when we grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.75,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:930790,932750}{\i1}Me, Jean's bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.25,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:932750,934252}{\i1}Fat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.58,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:934419,936588}{\i1}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:41.05,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:936588,941050}{\i1}Who would want to marry\Na weakling like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:46.09,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:941050,946097}{\i1}What do you know?\NIsabelle, you'll become my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.10,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:947015,949100}{\i1}Get off your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.73,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:958359,959736}Jean…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.03,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:959736,962030}You're that crybaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:05.95,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:962030,965950}That's right. Isabelle, do you remember\Nwhen I asked you to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.95,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:966492,967952}I've completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.78,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:967952,969787}Oh, this is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:14.16,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:969787,974167}Listen, Jean. Tonight, I've made\Nmy debut into the high society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.33,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:974167,976336}I can't play kids games\Nwith you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.33,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:976961,978338}Won't you dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.71,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:978588,980715}Not in a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.46,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:981341,983468}She hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.88,Default,Jean,0,0,0,,{TIME:983468,984886}Ha, that girl's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.88,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:984886,986888}Oh, do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.18,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:988932,990183}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.39,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:990183,993394}It's been two years since\Nyour engagement to Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:37.60,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:993394,997607}Now that you are an army captain,\Njust like my son Andréa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.44,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:997607,1000443}you've fully met the expectations\NI've set for my daughter's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.11,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000443,1003112}Mr. Rostain. Even though the aristocratic\Nworld is always dazzling,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:44.82,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003112,1004822}France is now in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.95,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005365,1008952}But it is evident\Nthat we will win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.41,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009994,1011412}I am a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.66,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011412,1013665}Andréa is fighting\Non the battlefield as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.04,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014040,1017043}I cannot selfishly seek happiness\Nin such a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:01.42,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017502,1021422}When this war is over,\NI will marry Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.96,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023383,1025969}{\i1}A marriage with Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.55,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025969,1027553}{\i1}But Jules…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027553,1030098}{\i1}What about Jules?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:15.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030098,1035353}{\i1}Geneviève wanted to escape\Nfrom the brilliant ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.65,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046406,1047657}Let us dance, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.53,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047657,1048533}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.36,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050118,1051369}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:04.15,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078604,1084152}{\i1}Victor could not imagine in his\Nworst nightmares that his fiancée Geneviève
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084152,1086738}{\i1}could be in love\Nwith another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.95,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088740,1091951}{\i1}Geneviève… You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.83,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093286,1095830}{\i1}Jules… I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:32.18,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109260,1112180}{\i1}I love you, Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.01,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113097,1116017}{\i1}Just a little longer.\NHold out just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:41.81,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117769,1121814}{\i1}If I was Victor's\Npartner in dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:03.96,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142794,1143961}Captain Langlois.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:07.54,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143961,1147548}I regretfully inform that you and your men\Nwill be joining the Paris garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.59,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147924,1149592}Yes, General Gambetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.80,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150426,1153805}Ladies and gentlemen,\Ncrème de la crème of the French society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:17.51,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153805,1157517}I am General Gambetta\Nfrom the French Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.68,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157517,1159685}We have fallen on hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:24.02,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159685,1164023}Our French Army suffered a crushing defeat\Nand surrendered in the Battle of Sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:28.11,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164023,1168111}Our Emperor Napoleon III was\Ntaken prisoner by the Prussian army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168611,1169737}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.65,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169737,1170655}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.32,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170655,1172323}How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.99,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172323,1173991}Silence, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.16,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173991,1177161}The Prussian army has started\Nto advance towards Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.99,Default,Gambetta,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177161,1180998}Paris is in crisis and needs immediate\Nmobilization of all available forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.88,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190925,1192885}Andréa…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.17,Default,Léon,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192885,1194178}Andréa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:54.92,Default,Marie,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194178,1194929}Andréa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.72,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194929,1197723}Ms. Rostain.\NPlease wake up. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.76,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198141,1200768}Andréa is not a man\Nwho would sell himself cheaply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.10,Default,Victor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200768,1203104}I am sure he's alive.\NHe will come back home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.57,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214157,1215575}Captain, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.70,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215575,1217702}Leave me here and go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.53,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217702,1218536}Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.49,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218536,1221497}Get up. Do you really want\Nto die in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.66,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221497,1224667}We're going back to Paris.\NWe're going to protect Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.21,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225376,1227211}We're going to protect Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.29,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227211,1229297}We're going to protect Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.21,Default,Andréa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229297,1231215}We're going to protect Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.28,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252486,1255281}Jules…\NWhat will happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.53,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255281,1257533}I wish I knew that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.70,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257533,1259702}But I feel like\Nsomething will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.95,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261329,1263956}Jules… I am scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:05.62,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263956,1265625}Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.91,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265625,1266918}Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.29,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266918,1268294}Don't let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.89,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283017,1284894}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.52,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285436,1287521}Sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.27,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287521,1289273}You and Victor…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.85,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289607,1290858}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.02,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290858,1293027}I can not help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.44,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293027,1295446}What I feel about\NJules is… It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:39.28,Default,Isabelle,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295780,1299283}I don't want to hear any of this!\NPoor Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.08,Default,Geneviève,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302578,1304080}Isabelle…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:52.12,Default,Gaston,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308793,1312129}Ms. Geneviève.\NThe carriage is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:56.05,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314090,1316050}You better go, Geneviève.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.97,Default,Jules,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319804,1321973}It is time to go, Geneviève.
