Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.26,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362096,1364265}{\i1}Jules was left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.93,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364265,1367935}{\i1}He just kept playing the piano.
